# Adding Reference Installation Photos

When new reference photos are added to `public/media/references/`, they MUST be added to **both** places in `src/pages/media.astro`:

## 1. `installations` array (Completed Projects gallery)

```js
{ name: 'First Last', location: 'City', capacity: 'X kW', inverter: 'Brand', panels: 'Brand', img: 'FILENAME.jpeg' },
```

Parse name, location, capacity, inverter brand, and panel brand directly from the filename.
Example: `ARUN-KOLLAM-5KW-SOLIS-INVERTER-PANELS-WAAREE.jpeg` → Arun, Kollam, 5 kW, Solis, Waaree

## 2. `allSlides` array (Solar — Beautifully Done slideshow)

```js
{ img: 'FILENAME.jpeg', caption: 'First Last — City', sub: 'X kW · Brand Inverter · Brand Panels' },
```

Both additions are mandatory — never add to one without the other.
